PN,44801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FA Stormont strategy aimed at ending
OL,7,Fviolence against women and girls in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland is making a real
OL,9,Fdifference, the first and deputy first
OL,10,Fministers have said.
OL,12,FMichelle O'Neill and Emma Little-
OL,13,FPengelly said the strategic framework
OL,14,Fwas never going to deliver a short-
OL,15,Fterm fix to what they described as a
OL,16,Fdeep-rooted cultural issue in society.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FThe Stormont leaders were attending
OL,7,Fthe launch of the seven-year
OL,8,Fstrategy's second delivery plan on
OL,9,FTuesday ` an event that heard
OL,10,Ftestimony from organisations involved
OL,11,Fin work on the ground, such as in
OL,12,Fschools and youth groups, to challenge
OL,13,Fmisogynist attitudes and tackle gender-
OL,14,Fbased violence, abuse and harm in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FThe leaders were asked to assess the
OL,7,Fimpact of the strategy two years on
OL,8,Ffrom its launch, amid public concern
OL,9,Fabout the number of women who continue
OL,10,Fto die in violence circumstances in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FThirty women have been killed since
OL,14,F2020 in the region, seven in the
OL,15,Fperiod since the strategy was launched
OL,16,Fin 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FMs O'Neill, who described violence
OL,7,Fagainst women and girls in Northern
OL,8,FIreland as a "scourge" and an
OL,9,F"epidemic", insisted the strategy was
OL,10,Fa priority for the Executive, with #5
OL,11,Fmillion spent to date and a plan to
OL,12,Fdirect a further #2 million during the
OL,13,Fsecond delivery phase, which runs
OL,14,Funtil 2028.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@VO]qD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"I think even today, when we reflect
OL,7,Fon testimony from some of the
OL,8,Forganisations that have been working
OL,9,Fin partnership with us, they have
OL,10,Freflected to us time and time again
OL,11,Fabout the difference the projects that
OL,12,Fthey're involved in are making on the
OL,13,Fground," said the First Minister.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"We have been ourselves out on the
OL,7,Fground, in with young people, in
OL,8,Fcommunity centres, in sports halls. We
OL,9,Fcan see that this is making a
OL,10,Fdifference. But the reality here is I
OL,11,Fwish there was a switch that we could
OL,12,Fjust flick and that we would solve
OL,13,Fthis problem. That's not the case.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"We have a cultural change to achieve
OL,7,Fin our society that's going to take
OL,8,Ftime. It's going to take persistence.
OL,9,FIt's going to take determination. And
OL,10,Fit's going to take partnership. And I
OL,11,Fknow that everybody in that room today
OL,12,Fwho's helped us to launch this plan,
OL,13,Fwho've delivered on the work so far,
OL,14,Fare determined to do so, and we're
OL,15,Fdetermined to support them in that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FWhile acknowledging uncertainty about
OL,7,Fthe overall Stormont budget, Ms
OL,8,FO'Neill insisted the #2 million
OL,9,Fearmarked for the next stage of the
OL,10,Fstrategy was a priority for the
OL,11,FExecutive Office.
OL,13,FMs Little-Pengelly said the strategy
OL,14,Fwas "never going to immediately end
OL,15,Fviolence against women and girls".
OL,17,FShe said the plan was focused on the
OL,18,F"key principle of prevention".
OL,20,F"That means starting early," said the
OL,21,Fdeputy First Minister.
OL,26,@vD@EOUwD@aO]zD@AOUzD@]O]|D@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"It means getting in there in terms of
OL,7,Fschools and youth groups and trying to
OL,8,Fchange, as we've said, those attitudes
OL,9,Fand issues that give rise to those
OL,10,Fbehaviours later in life.
OL,12,F"It's around supporting those
OL,13,Forganisations to work with women who
OL,14,Fare undergoing violence. Currently, it
OL,15,Fis about supporting those
OL,16,Forganisations working with families
OL,17,Fand communities that are having to
OL,18,Flive through the devastation of losing
OL,19,Ftheir loved one.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"Of course, the value in these
OL,7,Fstrategies and actions will be what
OL,8,Fyou don't see. It's those that do not
OL,9,Fget murdered. It's those that do not
OL,10,Flive with violence every day. And that
OL,11,Fis where we want to get to.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"But, of course, that will require `
OL,7,Fand we said this right from the outset
OL,8,F` it will require a long period of
OL,9,Fsustained investment. And, of course,
OL,10,Fit isn't just about that additional
OL,11,Fmoney ` that additional money is there
OL,12,Fto support research, to support
OL,13,Forganisations within the community
OL,14,Fsector, to support some of those
OL,15,Fsupport services ` but, of course,
OL,16,Fit's more than that. It's about
OL,17,Fmainstreaming these key principles and
OL,18,Fvalues within our education sector,
OL,19,Fwithin the health sector, within so
OL,20,Fmany other additional parts of
OL,21,Fgovernment."
OL,26,@nD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly suggested the
OL,7,Fresponse to the conviction of a man
OL,8,Flast year for harassing her online
OL,9,Fdemonstrated an attitude in society
OL,10,Fthat needed to change.
OL,12,F"I have to say, some of our newspapers
OL,13,Fetc barely referenced it," she said.
OL,15,F"You know, so when somebody who's a
OL,16,Fdeputy First Minister, jointly leading
OL,17,Fthis Executive, has somebody who's
OL,18,Fjailed for quite a period of time for
OL,19,Fa threat to kill, and yet there will
OL,20,Fbe focus on other issues.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@ZO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"To me, that is an indication that
OL,7,Fpeople are still not taking these
OL,8,Fissues seriously. People do not
OL,9,Funderstand the impact that that has on
OL,10,Fa woman, on a person, in terms of the
OL,11,Ffear that people feel about that. And
OL,12,Fthese things have to be taken
OL,13,Fseriously. It's one example, I
OL,14,Fpersonally experienced it."
OL,16,FMs O'Neill said the strategy "means
OL,17,Feverything" to her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@[O]xD@^OUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"I'm a woman, I'm a mummy, I'm a
OL,7,Fgranny, and what I want is that my
OL,8,Fdaughter or my granddaughter grows up
OL,9,Fin a world where there's fairness,
OL,10,Fwhere they're safe, where they feel
OL,11,Fsafe, where they don't have to mind
OL,12,Fthemselves all the time just because
OL,13,Fof their gender," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776870667
OL,3,CStrategy to end violence against women
OL,4,Cand girls 'making a real difference'
OL,6,F"So this goes to the heart of the kind
OL,7,Fof society that we want to live in and
OL,8,Fthe kind of society that we want to
OL,9,Fbuild. And that's why this work is so
OL,10,Fimportant. I wish it was fast work.
OL,11,FBut the reality is, it's not, because
OL,12,Fyou're changing decades of culture.
OL,13,FYou're changing what is really right
OL,14,Fat the heart of the culture of
OL,15,Fsociety."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/16
